/api.github.com/users/schiesbn/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-08-13t07:29:35z","updated_at":"2013-08-13t09:23:14z","body":"i just updated the documentation and thought about it a bit. because we expire old deleted files if a file gets moved to the trash and if a new file was added to your owncloud, we make sure that you will never run out of memory because of to many files in your trash bin. therefore i don't think that a cronjob will add any additional value."}]